  "detailed_description": "<strong>Become a hero in a thrilling horror adventure:</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3003720/extras/55429e5fa03d34a4251dd705912f85f5.avif?t=1759167270\" width=600 height=338 /></span><br>Courage: ZaGame puts you in the shoes of a courageous protagonist navigating through a haunting world filled with mysteries and challenges. Your goal is to uncover the secrets and survive the horrors lurking around every corner.<br><br><strong>Engage in intense gameplay:</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3003720/extras/a43299850d6bceb9982055959db30fe9.avif?t=1759167270\" width=600 height=338 /></span><br>With various challenges and puzzles, players must use their wits and bravery to overcome obstacles. The game features a range of weapons and tools to aid in your journey, ensuring a dynamic and engaging experience.<br><br><strong>Explore and survive:</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3003720/extras/f2ac3ca1da00d72f66c6b5ec69914534.avif?t=1759167270\" width=600 height=338 /></span><br>Explore detailed environments, each with its own unique atmosphere and dangers. The game's immersive graphics and sound design create a chilling experience that keeps players on the edge of their seats.<br><br><strong>An original horror story:</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3003720/extras/2c6e3576057574e6e2af997c40cad7ea.poster.avif?t=1759167270\" width=352 height=288 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3003720/extras/2c6e3576057574e6e2af997c40cad7ea.webm?t=1759167270\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3003720/extras/2c6e3576057574e6e2af997c40cad7ea.mp4?t=1759167270\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Dive into a gripping narrative that blends horror and adventure. Courage: ZaGame offers a unique storyline that keeps players engaged and eager to uncover the next twist.<br><br><strong>Get ready to experience the fear and excitement of Courage: ZaGame!</strong>",
